This program is used to save and recover the permissions for every files(include files, subdir, files in subdir) in one certain path.
The program will save the permissions to the file "s-perm" in the same dir with this program itself. When recover the permissions, the program will read the permissions from file "s-perm" and recover them to corresponding files.

Usage: 
sr-perm.py path -s/-r 
path: our processing object, we will save and recover the permissions for the files in it. It can be absolute path and relative path.
-s: save
-r: recover

